title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 14 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 14 2022
description:
Biden claims 40-year high inflation shows "progress." Buck says, "Seems like the Democrats' pitch is, 'Vote for us because we've made things slightly less awful than the few months before.'" What in your life is better since Biden has been president? Biden: "If Republicans win, inflation is going to get worse. It’s that simple." Clay describes wonderful painting from listener that he tweeted out and that is on ClayAndBuck.com. Highlights of Tudor Dixon debating Democrat Gov. Gretchen Whitmer of Michigan. C&B stress again how little they think of Whitmer. What would you do in Animal Thunderdome: man vs. cougar?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
